---
---

<section id="sobre" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Sobre Mí</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-pink-600 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Descripción -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Soy un desarrollador apasionado con experiencia en tecnologías web modernas. Me especializo en crear aplicaciones robustas, intuitivas y escalables que resuelven problemas reales.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Mi objetivo es combinar diseño atractivo con funcionalidad impecable, entregando siempre resultados de calidad profesional. Creo en la importancia de la experiencia del usuario y en escribir código limpio y mantenible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Estadísticas -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">50+</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600 font-medium">Proyectos Completados</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-2">30+</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600 font-medium">Clientes Satisfechos</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">5+</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600 font-medium">Años de Experiencia</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Info items -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
      <div class="group p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-indigo-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-pink-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Desarrollo</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Full Stack Development con tecnologías modernas</p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-indigo-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-pink-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Diseño</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">UI/UX Design con enfoque en experiencia del usuario</p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-indigo-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-pink-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Innovación</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Soluciones creativas y propuestas de valor</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
